data.description: This Traditional 3-2-2 is Devine with beautiful finishes and upgrades built in 2021.   Kitchen has all Soft close white cabinets and drawers, nice size pantry, breakfast bar, deep granite composite sink, granite counter tops, newer Range,  Stainless Steel Dishwasher and French Door Refrigerator.  Reverse Osmosis water at the sink and soft water treatment system to home. Open concept with luxury vinyl plank and led lighting through out. Master Suite with dual sinks and closets. Ceiling fans and Low E window . Three solar tubes provide natural light in addition to decorative lighting. Laundry room with sink complete with washer and dryer included.  Large covered patio, paved brick sitting area with privacy fence for entertaining or relaxing. Radiant barrier roof sheathing, foam insulated walls and roof deck for lower utility bills  All masonry exterior. Beautifully landscaped. Oversized garage with side exit door.  Appliances convey. Owner to pay 1000.00 of buyers closing costs.
